    <td class="roweven" valign="top" nowrap><i>2006-08-11</i></td>
    <td class="roweven" valign="top" nowrap>7.0</td>
    <td class="roweven" valign="top"><i><a href="/account/profile.php?user_id=10614">Luis Caamano</a></i></td>
    <td class="roweven" valign="top" width="2000">Added ';' to findfile() call to make sure we always search upwards.&nbsp;&nbsp;There are some cases where findfile() doesn't find the ChangeLog file if the semicolon is not added to the path to search.<br></td>
</tr>
